<Panel xmlns="urn:import:com.vaadin.ui" xmlns:p="urn:vaadin:parent" xmlns:ef="urn:import:com.stpl.ifs.ui" xmlns:ep="urn:import:org:asi:ui:extfilteringtable:paged">
    <VerticalLayout margin="true" spacing = "true" width="100%" height="100%">
        <Panel caption = "Search Criteria" width="100%" height="100%">
            <HorizontalLayout spacing="true" margin="true" immediate="true">
                <GridLayout spacing="true"  immediate="true" columns="2" rows="1">
                    <Label value="View Name" immediate="true" />
                    <TextField id="viewNameEX"/>
                </GridLayout>
            </HorizontalLayout>
        </Panel>
        <HorizontalLayout margin="true" spacing = "true">
            <Button id="searchButtonEX" caption = "SEARCH" />
            <Button id="resetButtonEX" caption = "RESET" />
        </HorizontalLayout>
        <Panel caption = "Results" width="100%" height="100%">
            <VerticalLayout id ="resultsTableLayoutEX" width="100%" height="100%">                
            </VerticalLayout>
        </Panel>
        <HorizontalLayout margin="true" spacing = "true">
            <Button id="selectButtonEX" caption = "SELECT" />
            <Button id="closeButtonEX" caption = "CLOSE" />
        </HorizontalLayout>
    </VerticalLayout>
</Panel>